products.title: Harriet Vintage Curtain
products.description: Harriet, a beautiful bird themed pattern bursting with colour at a great price. These multicoloured curtains are perfect to add a bird theme to any room in your home, the array of colours in the pattern means it will fit in with most decor. Product id: db-cur0875 fabric colour: vintage material: 100% cotton lining: light filtering poly/cotton blended lining energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - increase to er3 (high) by adding thermal lining light filtering: yes harriet vintage curtain in cream/brown/multicoloured.
